<h3>Welcome to&nbsp;OCHP!</h3>
<p><img src="/images/Kristen_Kleppe_Web01.jpg" alt="Kristen Kleppe Web01" width="138" height="183" style="float: left; padding-right: 15px;" />Thank you for visiting&nbsp;our website.&nbsp;We hope this will be your first step on a path&nbsp;towards health and healing and that you will allow us to help as you move forward. Psychotherapy can be a wonderful experience of positive growth and transformation - let's talk about&nbsp;how we can make that happen for you.</p>
<p>We&nbsp;look at therapy as not only curing that "which ails you" but helping you evolve into your highest potential.</p>
<p>Kristin Kleppe, Psy.D, President</p>
